HEADWORD: Coraciiformes
<hw>Coraciiformes</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>an order of
birds including the rollers; kingfishers; hornbills; hoopoes; motmots;
bee-eaters; todies.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Coraciiformes</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
